    "extras": [
      "Indian passport visa rules can vary by residence status and supporting visas, so verify the current Morocco e-Visa or consular process before booking flights.",
      "ONCF trains are the smoothest way to do Casablanca and Marrakech, but Chefchaouen, Essaouira, and Merzouga rely on CTM, Supratours, or grand taxis.",
      "Carry small cash for medina tickets, tannery tips, and bus station snacks because card acceptance drops outside bigger hotels and modern restaurants.",
      "Friday mosque access and some monument hours shift around prayer times, and Ramadan changes food-service timing after sunset.",
      "Merzouga gets cold after dark from November to February, so keep a fleece or light down layer even if Marrakech felt warm."
    ],
